    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed per the credibility plan, consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device. CFD hemolysis predictions demonstrate mean relative error of 8.3% against FDA benchmark data, satisfying the 15% acceptance criterion. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device submission.",
